descriptionHtml:
You will find a spell on the steps that will teleport you to Mythical Garden to get the spell you need to go to Mythical Garden using the console.

Console code: COC Mythical_Garden_Cell_001

When you get there at the bottom off the steps to your [size=1][s]right[/s][/size] liftside going down is the spell.

You can use fast travel or use statue of mara

----------------------------------
REQUIREMENTS:
hearthfire

----------------------------------

RECOMMENDED MODS:
More plants [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26851/]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26851/[/url]?
